Package edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.recommendationgenerator

Class RecommendedInstanceImpl

java.lang.Object
edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.recommendationgenerator.RecommendedInstanceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Claimant, RecommendedInstance, NounMappingChangeListener
public class RecommendedInstanceImpl extends Object implements RecommendedInstance, Claimant, NounMappingChangeListener
This class represents recommended instances. These instances should be contained by the model. The likelihood is measured by the probability. Every recommended instance has a unique name.
